node.text: The @Roger_Dubuis Excalibur Spider Pirelli 🔥🔥 The ingenious Quick Release System allow easy and quick interchangeability of all three components of the watch - from bezel, crown to strap, with a simple click. Available with three additional kits in red, white or blue – the inimitable Pirelli color codes, to get the watch transformed from a full black to a pop of bold color, in a click. Another cool feature is the strap which is made of winning motorsport tyre rubber from real races 🏁 #RogerDubuis #NoRulesOurGame #Pirelli
